                    <span>This was an interesting and informative book.  It was easy to read, and gave lots of visual examples of how different people organize differently.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Worth reading!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
